    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n50(1+6\\%)^n &> 100 \\\\\n\\Leftrightarrow 50 \\cdot 1,06^n &> 100 \\\\\n\\Leftrightarrow 1,06^n &> 2 \\\\\n\\Leftrightarrow n &> \\log_{1,06} 2 = 11,9\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
